{
  "texts": [
    "The best accuracy and precision were registered for SVM across these topics.",
    "While the textual features showed their effectiveness, other studies have suggested using user features.",
    "El Balloul et al. [64] proposed a model called (CAT) for the credibility analysis of Arabic content on Twitter.",
    "CAT is built using a combination of features related to content and user.",
    "It has 26 content-based features and 22 user-based features."
  ]
}